<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Activate Your Amazing Shopping Account</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; } .email-container { max-width:
      600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .email-header {
      background-color: #212121; color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 20px; text-align:
      center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; } .email-header h1 { font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; } .email-body { padding:
      30px 20px; text-align: center; } .email-body p { font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; } .cta-button {
      background-color: #212121; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding:
      12px 24px; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; } .cta-button:hover { background-color:
      #333333; } .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center;
      padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; font-size: 14px; } .footer a {
      color: #212121; text-decoration: none; } .footer p { color: #888; }
      .footer .brand-name { font-weight: bold; color: #212121; } .contact-info {
      background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; font-size:
      16px; margin: 20px 0; } .contact-info strong { color: #212121; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='email-header'>
        <h1>Welcome to Amazing Shopping Online!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='email-body'>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up at Amazing Shopping Online! To activate your
          account, please click the button below:</p>
        <a href={{activationLink}} class='cta-button'>Activate Your Account</a>
        <p>If you did not register for an account, simply ignore this email.</p>

        <div class='contact-info'>
          <p><strong>Headquarters:</strong>
            440 Đ. Nguyễn Văn Luông, Phường 12, Quận 6, Hồ Chí Minh</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 093 9382315</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to
          <a href='https://youtube.com/@hoidanit' target='_blank'>contact us</a>.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being part of the Amazing Shopping Online community!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>